cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image synthesis and uses deep learning techniques to generate pseudo healthy images from pathological ones. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also uses adversarial training, which is a popular technique in deep learning and falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also mentions the use of segmentation masks, which is a common technique in medical image analysis (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on two medical image datasets, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) category.
